Steps to run this : 

1. Install Xampp
2. Start Apache and Mysql server
3. Put this project inside the Xampp/htdocs/
4. Goto your browser and open http://localhost/phpmyadmin/
5. Create a new database with name mydb
6. Goto your browser and open localhost/Web_Form_Php_MySql
7. Enter your details 
8. Click submit
9. Open http://localhost/phpmyadmin/ and check the submitted Info
10. Export Info using export tab as CSV
